::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504033058: Config/Level/Mission/5040330/Act/Act504033058.json-->
::'''Vipsania:''' Ahem, hello there, friend... Want some seeds?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are seeds?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043703-->
:::'''Vipsania:''' Some research outcomes from the Grove. With Cerces' blessing, we have stored our efforts into special "seeds," and are granting permission to certain groups to read them.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You got a license for this?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043705-->
:::'''Vipsania:''' What kind of question is that? This is officially authorized by the Grove, and I pay my taxes to the Council of Elders every Month of Fortune.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504043706-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043706-->
::'''Vipsania:''' You look bewildered, though it's a common sight to those living near the Garden. You must be new to Okhema?
::'''Vipsania:''' Allow me to introduce myself: I am Vipsania, Grove of Epiphany Financial Officer. But now... just think of me as a Grove Knowledge salesperson... Mm, my sister would say I'm "peddling wares."
::'''Vipsania:''' Since you haven't been in Okhema for long, how would you like to take home some "seeds"? They're all precious treasures from the Grove. How about it, care for some?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} "Knowledge" can be sold too?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043710-->
:::'''Vipsania:''' Of course! It may not be possible for ordinary people, but how hard can it be with the Titan's divinity? We've only been graced by Cerces' light, retaining slivers of their omniscience.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504043715-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043715-->
:::'''Vipsania:''' Oh yes, you know of the Grove of Epiphany, yes? Everyone says that we house all the brightest minds in Amphoreus. But don't listen to all that horn-tooting. At its heart, experimentation builds the foundation of knowledge. Without money or platform, even the smartest scholar is a fool.
:::'''Vipsania:''' I'm not one of those scoundrels reselling Grove assets. These are Sunken Tree Seeds that I regularly procure to see if they help with our daily lives. Only successful product tests are sold on the market.
:::'''Vipsania:''' Moreover, I'm also promoting the spread of knowledge. Cerces' spirit guides us, for us to share their knowledge with even more people. Of course, their disciples must first be able to put food on their tables.
:::'''Vipsania:''' How about it, do you want to contribute to spreading the knowledge of Okhema?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Gimme some.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043720-->
::::'''Vipsania:''' Great, you're decisive. Let me take a look at my stock. I do have quite a few popular products on hand. I remember there's something that can double crop yields and another that can treat household wastewater...
::::'''Vipsania:''' Strange... Why did the teleslate go silent? Let me double check...
::::'''Vipsania:''' ...
::::'''Vipsania:''' Drats, there's something wrong with the teleslate. I didn't manage to link up with the Grove. I'll holler when I fix it, for now I'll put you on the reservation list, so sorry about that...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Knowledge only hurts my brain, sorry...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043725-->
::::'''Vipsania:''' ...
::::'''Vipsania:''' Plenty have turned down my sales pitch, but this reason is a first. No wonder some people fail to grasp the spirit of Cerces &mdash; now I'm beginning to see why.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504043727-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043727-->
:::'''Vipsania:''' What a pity, such a great opportunity yet I failed to close a deal. Ah, it's all on me for not preparing...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's got an internet vibe to it!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043712-->
:::'''Vipsania:''' Huh? What net? You mean the World Wound Web?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504043715-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504043715-->
